{"tid":535650,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"［多圖］［戀童癖］12歲蘿莉戀24歲歌手　5年過去「想婚了」","createTime":"2018-01-21T05:39:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-07T12:33:05.000Z","uid":121393,"like":239,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"238e2ea27ded5b582f96256bef2b3d4c5d33eae1","tid":535650,"uid":121393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T05:39:22.000Z","msg":"中國歌手張木易2012年時爆出與12歲的混血女孩AKAMA MIKI相戀，2人經常在《微博》上高調放閃，女方還曾公開表示到16歲就要嫁給他，這段相差12歲的戀情讓許多人無法接受，更被挨轟有「<blockquote>戀童癖</blockquote>」，然而5年過去了，2人感情不受影響仍然甜蜜，更表示即將攜手步入禮堂。<br />\n《51新聞》指出，AKAMA MIKI的父母在她8歲時，請來張木易當音樂老師而相識。兩人在第一次時就對彼此一見鍾情，不時見面通信長達4年，等到Miki12歲的時候，才決定公開戀情，當時張木易率先在《微博》公開兩人親密照，接著Miki就在微博甜蜜互動，戀情曝光後讓不少人十分訝異。<br />\nAKAMA MIKI曾在《微博》表示等到16歲就嫁給張木易，但因為引來很多批評已經刪除留言。來自加拿大的AKAMA MIKI是中、日、德三國混血，曾參加新絲路中國少兒模特大賽獲得全國總決賽冠軍；張木易是香港國際星集團「北京世紀博灣」旗下的唱作藝人，因為藝人身分，這段被中國網友誇飾為「跨越一甲子」的戀情，也傳出有炒作之嫌。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/21/133602_c19e1446e77ca94a57a98710e7eb3810.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F21%2F133602_c19e1446e77ca94a57a98710e7eb3810.jpg&h=b2b4f595&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/21/133603_fb3196918dba2cd6e83eb5ff53a117ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F21%2F133603_fb3196918dba2cd6e83eb5ff53a117ac.jpg&h=0c86608a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/21/133603_582df2f8a20aba4206b4acb4e11d86a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F21%2F133603_582df2f8a20aba4206b4acb4e11d86a9.jpg&h=dde453d8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/21/133604_582df2f8a20aba4206b4acb4e11d86a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F21%2F133604_582df2f8a20aba4206b4acb4e11d86a9.jpg&h=2811aa7c&s={SIZE}\" />